  "detailed_description": "A collection of 4 small games from The Voices Games<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAyleouna:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA combination of 3d and 2d platforming where you jump between planets and gravity pads with their own gravity in space with twin stick shooting.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLizard Lady vs The Cats:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA 3rd person shooter where you kill all the enemies to open the exit from the level.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLady in a Leotard With a Gun<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA 3rd person shooter where you kill all the enemies to open the exit from the level.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSpectrewoods:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA horror themed 3rd person shooter where you follow the flowers which grow out of the ground when you get near to reach the exit",
